



---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Experience from "../components/ExperienceCard.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experience - Amna Rafi">
  <main>
    <div class="page-hero scroll-reveal">
      <h1 class="page-title">Experience</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        I enjoy being part of collaborative environments where ideas flow freely, and everyone contributes to building meaningful products. Transparency, adaptability, and open communication are values I deeply appreciate, as they foster creativity, teamwork, and impactful outcomes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
    <Experience
      title="Product Analyst at US Mobile, Lahore"
      description="Collaborated with engineering, design, and support teams to prioritize roadmap initiatives, driving a 15% increase in CSAT. Led analysis of 1,000+ support tickets and feedback items, uncovering product gaps that informed new feature opportunities across the mobile service platform. Identified recurring pain points that helped cut churn risk and improve customer retention."
      subtitle="July 2025 – Present"
      image="/images/logos/usmobile_logo.jpeg"
    />

    <Experience
      title="Product Designer at The Essential Studios, Islamabad"
      description="Built scalable design systems and component libraries in Figma, setting consistent standards that improved collaboration between design and development teams. Presented research-backed recommendations that influenced 3 key roadmap decisions, ensuring a user-centered product strategy. Delivered complete documentation including user flows, interaction specifications, and responsive guidelines that streamlined onboarding for new developers and accelerated design-to-development cycles."
      subtitle="May 2024 – June 2025"
      image="/images/logos/essential_studio.jpeg"
    />

    <Experience
      title="Web Development Internee at Web3gle, Lahore"
      description="Designed and implemented responsive user interfaces using React.js and Tailwind CSS, improving user retention by 30%. Conducted systematic A/B testing on UI components to validate design decisions and optimize conversion funnels for e-commerce clients. Collaborated with designers to translate mockups into pixel-perfect, accessible web interfaces. Improved website performance by 25% through code optimization and responsive design best practices."
      subtitle="June 2024 – August 2024"
    />

    <Experience
      title="UI/UX Designer Intern at Septem Systems, Lahore"
      description="Developed wireframes, mockups, and high-fidelity prototypes using Figma for web and mobile applications. Conducted usability testing sessions and iterated designs based on user feedback and analytics data. Contributed to building and maintaining design systems to ensure consistency across multiple product touchpoints."
      subtitle="March 2024 – April 2024"
      image="/images/logos/code_alpha_logo.jpeg"
    />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    max-width: 70ch;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .timeline {
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>